    <section class="highlight">
      <div class="content-section">
        <div class="highlight-text">
          <p>We conduct long-term research to understand how Southwestern rangeland ecosystems are changing and to understand the fundamental mechanisms of ecosystem change in arid rangelands globally. We facilitate research on the Jornada Experimental Range (JER) by many other researchers.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
